		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've created a simple test-ROM for sprite behaviour aimed at (beginner)-emulator developers. I needed it myself so I thought perhaps there might be others interested aswell. It allows you to change h/v-flipping and 8x8/8x16 spritemode and see it's appeareance on screen.<br />Tested on real (PAL) NES and it works.

		
